  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/a2082462a1e79142198cef3f7b88f53e.avif?t=1762380865\" width=601 height=185 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/4fe947af810a4050b43ea6cd74974097.poster.avif?t=1762380865\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/4fe947af810a4050b43ea6cd74974097.webm?t=1762380865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/4fe947af810a4050b43ea6cd74974097.mp4?t=1762380865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready to laugh and blast through 100 physics-based maps in this comedic multiplayer FPS game. With wacky weapons and fast-paced action, it's a hilarious and explosive experience for you and your friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/b5b040a7e920eb7f97ec3408b129c4ed.avif?t=1762380865\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with 3 other blasters, either friends or random (all wrigglin' around)<br></li><li>Chaotic physics based guns <br></li><li>100+ Chaotic physics maps (with destructive maps for destructive people)<br></li><li>Quick in-game chat (distract n' kill lol)<br></li><li>Who doesn't like blackholes and stuff?<br></li><li>Make someone go boom (sus bomb)<br></li><li>Noodle limbs (cuz why not)<br></li><li>Punch with your noodle hands</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/4fe947af810a4050b43ea6cd74974097.poster.avif?t=1762380865\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/4fe947af810a4050b43ea6cd74974097.webm?t=1762380865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/4fe947af810a4050b43ea6cd74974097.mp4?t=1762380865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready to laugh and blast through 100 physics-based maps in this comedic multiplayer FPS game. With wacky weapons and fast-paced action, it's a hilarious and explosive experience for you and your friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071420/extras/b5b040a7e920eb7f97ec3408b129c4ed.avif?t=1762380865\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with 3 other blasters, either friends or random (all wrigglin' around)<br></li><li>Chaotic physics based guns <br></li><li>100+ Chaotic physics maps (with destructive maps for destructive people)<br></li><li>Quick in-game chat (distract n' kill lol)<br></li><li>Who doesn't like blackholes and stuff?<br></li><li>Make someone go boom (sus bomb)<br></li><li>Noodle limbs (cuz why not)<br></li><li>Punch with your noodle hands</li></ul>",
